description:
Dr. Bronner’s has been doing it right for decades. What’s "it" you ask? In this case, the answer is an all-natural and unscented baby soap that’s well-suited for sensitive skin. Just dilute a few drops on a wet wash cloth, lather, and avoid the eyes for a tear-free clean at bath time.Formulation is fragrance-free with double the olive oil of standard Br. Bronner's soap.Biodegradable.Made with organic and certified fair trade ingredients.Bottle is made from 100% recycled materials.Concentrated. A few drops into a washcloth is all that's needed.Not tear-free. Keep out of baby's eyes.

